	설명 : After many years of being faithful to one another in marriage, Harry_s wife Tara decided for her birthday to undertake the darkest and yet most fantasized scenario every married man envisions; a threesome. For months, she talked about and planned and even had a candidate, her friend Ruby. She does not know that the two are married, and that_s how she wants him to act; he walks in, pretends not to know Tara, and attempts to win her and her friend over with his charm and sexual bravado. But even the most well-made plans can have snags, for if Harry fails, there are plenty of others in the bar that night who may be up to the task. GAMEPLAY Hot Wife Tara is a choose your own adventure story that puts you in the shoes of Harry, a married man who, along with his wife, Tara, want to embark on a sexual journey together. With multiple branching paths and eight unique endings, can you help Harry ensure that his wife has the best birthday of her life? FEATURES: - stunning 4k resolution [3840 x 2160px] - sensual and smooth 40 frames animations for sex scenes - 250 static images and 30 sex animations - erotic plot with over 30.000 words - non-linear gameplay with 6 endings to achieve - for trophy hunters: sex scenes and endings gallery - 100% UNCENSORED!', True, 5, 'games_image_22.png', '1718466009268-c0376243-455b-4daa-a7af-f767e8302b01.png');
INSERT INTO post (user_id, title, content, is_open, category_id, original_filename, stored_filename) VALUES (7, 'The Summit High School: Prologue Episode', '	개발자 : GLOBINS
