INSERT INTO post (user_id, title, content, is_open, category_id, original_filename, stored_filename) VALUES (8, 'Illusion of Being - Adult Rated - Chapter 1', '	개발자 : True Element Games
	장르 : Adventure,Casual,Indie,Simulation
	설명 : On our Steam discussion boards you will find more details about the game and free content! / Tell Us About The Game_s Story The main character is a professor at a local community college. He has a wife that he has been with for eleven years, and a nine year old daughter. They have created the normal life that many strive for... nice car, nice house, good jobs.... However, the last year has brought some concern to light for our main character. His wife has become more distant, reserved, and indulgent. He contemplates that he is overthinking it all. When he brings the topic up to his wife, she calls him crazy and states how busy she has been with work. However things are not okay in this seemingly normal suburban home. Our main character discovers his wife_s affair and that is where _Illusion of Being_ really digs in. Our main character is forced to make choices he wishes he never had to. Will he succumb to depression and possibly upset those who care for him? Will he embrace the single life and have more attention than he ever thought possible? Will he find true love within his new found freedom? As the player, the choices are yours to make... All the rewards as well as possible consequences, are yours to experience.... Why did we make Illusion of Being? Illusion of Being was made to bring back the story telling that we crave while also bringing you some of the most intense visuals and emotions that a story like this can convey. It approaches difficult subjects on many different levels from substance abuse, adultery, friendship, betrayal, lust, fantasy, and much more! The game highlights elements that we believe have not been explored before in a detailed adult visual novel. It is grounded, real, immersive, heart breaking, inspiring.... With some of the best animations and characterization within the genre to accompany the tale. We aimed to create something both thought provoking, emotional, and yet thrilling to experience. Illusion of Being Chapter 1 is just the beginning of this journey, there is still so much more to come! Game Highlights - Branching story paths that matter - - Story and animations are presented cinematically - - Sweeping movie-like soundtrack that conveys emotion - - Choices that can greatly affect how the story unfolds - - Realistically modeled characters that have depth and story arcs - - Almost all renders will be unique, very few repeating backgrounds - - Many unlockable SFW and NSFW renders - - A wealth of content including in-game achievements and galleries - - Timed hidden object events to find extra content and unlockables - - Cinematic and immersive H-Scenes with multiple angles - - Mini games - - Full story will be 4 chapters -', True, 5, 'games_image_34.png', '1718466009270-a13d01a2-3e7d-4496-8324-59c3e854959c.png');
